          "Howdy!",
          "Welcome my friend.",
          "Hey there!",
          "Hello!",
          "Bonjour!",
        ]}
      />
      <p>
        I'm Farshad üëãüèº! I'm a musician and teacher who's been coding for two
        years. I have a passion for building useful, joyful, accessible apps and
