      <Image
        class="profile-image"
        src={profileImage}
        alt="profile"
        width={200}
        height={200}
      />
    </div>
    <RecentPosts />
  </div>
  <p>
    This is a little website and blog where I write about my coding journey,
    things I'm working on, showcase projects, and do other nerdy things. I focus
    mostly on tech and developer stuff, but I may veer into my other interests
    too. If you're looking for music and/or are not sure what all this is about,
    check out my
    <a href="https://farshadzadeh.com">other website</a>.
